  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110149684995\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110149684995\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121016_89/isuhani_1350388155525nBwGd_JPEG/%C0%FC%C4%A7%B0%FA_%BD%C4%C0%CC_SCI_%C0%FA%B3%CE.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"253\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 341px\" id=\"20121016_89/isuhani_1350388155525nBwGd_JPEG/%C0%FC%C4%A7%B0%FA_%BD%C4%C0%CC_SCI_%C0%FA%B3%CE.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A56ECF03')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121016_89/isuhani_1350388155525nBwGd_JPEG/%C0%FC%C4%A7%B0%FA_%BD%C4%C0%CC_SCI_%C0%FA%B3%CE.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">이수한의원 문학진 원장님께서 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">공동연구한</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\"> 내용이 실린&nbsp;</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">SCI</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">급 국제 과학저널.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">전침을 꾸준히 시술하였을 때 스트레스호르몬의 분비는 정상범위이고, 식욕억제물질은 분비가 증가하여</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">식사량이 줄고, 체중 조절도 잘 되었다는 연구 내용입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">전침 치료로 스트레스 없이 식사조절과 체중조절이 가능하다는 결과로 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">체중과 건강유지에 전침이 효과적임을 입증한 연구입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 4.32pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
